00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:48,560
Louder.

608
00:29:50,360 --> 00:29:51,520
Thank you, Mom.

609
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:01,440
I'll always be your mother.

610
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,740
