661
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:47,540
You got beaten?

662
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:52,240
Where did you steal all that money from?

663
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,520
All for you.

664
00:32:56,280 --> 00:32:56,960
No.

665
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:57,720
Listen to me.

666
00:32:59,440 --> 00:33:01,480
I feel terrible inside.

667
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:02,440
You know?

668
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:03,680
What's wrong?

669
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:07,560
My mother passed away.

670
00:33:09,560 --> 00:33:10,920
My mother

671
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:13,530
