672
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:14,880
She's gone.

673
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:16,800
[Sob]

674
00:33:17,600 --> 00:33:19,840
Do you understand what I mean?

675
00:33:20,080 --> 00:33:22,120
I feel so awful inside.

676
00:33:22,440 --> 00:33:23,880
My mother is gone.

677
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:25,680
In this whole wide world,

678
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:29,680
I can't find anyone to talk to.

679
00:33:29,680 --> 00:33:31,520
Someone to talk to.

680
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:33,280
I'm here.

681
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:34,280
Always have been.

682
00:33:46,120 --> 00:33:47,080
You all eat first.

683
00:33:47,080 --> 00:33:48,680
I'll go find Cui Xiaohong.

684
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:55,120
Let's eat.

685
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:59,640
Oh my!

686
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:00,320
I'm here.

687
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:01,240
What the hell?

688
00:34:03,320 --> 00:34:04,450
About your brother,

689
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:06,720
