690
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:09,000
His temper is way too explosive.

691
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,920
Why does he resort to violence?

692
00:34:10,920 --> 00:34:13,760
My brother beat you up?

693
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:14,760
What? Beat me?

694
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:16,600
How could he possibly beat me?

695
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:19,520
Why did my brother

696
00:34:19,520 --> 00:34:20,980
Why did my brother hit you?

697
00:34:22,159 --> 00:34:23,080
Well,

698
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,719
we were talking about you.

699
00:34:24,719 --> 00:34:25,800
We had a misunderstanding,

700
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:26,920
and then he started fighting.

701
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,000
Talking about me?

702
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,080
What about?

703
00:34:29,080 --> 00:34:30,440
What were you saying about me?

704
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,600
Just that

705
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:34,480
life abroad hasn't been easy for you.

706
00:34:35,800 --> 00:34:36,239
Come on,

707
00:34:36,239 --> 00:34:37,320
let's drink.

708
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:39,719
A toast to your hard times abroad.

709
00:34:39,719 --> 00:34:41,120
Cheers.

710
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:47,040
Hong.

711
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:48,600
Don't get so close.

712
00:34:48,600 --> 00:34:49,600
It's irritating.

713
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,679
Later,

714
00:34:53,159 --> 00:34:54,080
