715
00:34:54,080 --> 00:34:55,360
I have a modest car.

716
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:56,489
I can give you a ride.

717
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:03,720
You'll drive me?

718
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:04,840
I'll drive you.

719
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:05,880
And then?

720
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:07,840
Then,

721
00:35:08,360 --> 00:35:10,620
we could go to my place and chat a bit more.

722
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:14,600
Get lost!

723
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:16,440
I know why my brother beat you up.

724
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:19,480
I know why my brother hit you.

725
00:35:20,560 --> 00:35:21,600
What did you just say?

726
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:22,130
Nothing.

727
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:23,600
Have a drink.

728
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,160
Oh my,

729
00:35:24,160 --> 00:35:24,840
