730
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:25,360
You can't hold your liquor.

731
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,160
Come on, let's drink.

732
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:26,520
Come on,

733
00:35:26,520 --> 00:35:27,760
let's drink.

734
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:28,600
Cheers!

735
00:35:28,600 --> 00:35:30,520
Drink up.

736
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:34,120
That song is mine.

737
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:34,760
Don't sing it.

738
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:35,760
That's my song.

739
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,360
It's nothing.

740
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,480
Can someone play it again for me?

741
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:42,160
Play it again.

742
00:37:16,120 --> 00:37:17,450
You're eating too fast.

743
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:19,120
They don't have this abroad.

744
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:22,360
The taste from childhood is still the best.

745
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:23,280
When we were little,

746
00:37:23,280 --> 00:37:25,040
we used to wrap it up bit by bit.

747
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:26,120
Now you

748
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:27,610
must be really wealthy.

749
00:37:29,640 --> 00:37:30,900
You don't understand.

750
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:34,690
Every bite I take is one less I'll have.

751
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:41,040
Does Erpang visit Huo Dongfeng often?

752
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:42,920
About three or four times

753
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,080
a year.

754
00:37:46,080 --> 00:37:47,200
What about you?

755
00:37:48,160 --> 00:37:49,400
I used to go often,

756
00:37:49,680 --> 00:37:51,320
but they've changed the rules recently.

757
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:52,580
Only immediate family

758
00:37:52,720 --> 00:37:53,440
