775
00:38:46,080 --> 00:38:47,410
I don't want your money.

776
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,880
Open it and see.

777
00:39:02,680 --> 00:39:03,960
I've changed my name

778
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:07,480
