779
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,760
Cui Qianhui.

780
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:15,320
Better than Baihui.

781
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:18,180
A thousand is greater than a hundred.

782
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,640
My son

783
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,860
