787
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:39,920
There are many things I haven't told my family.

788
00:39:44,280 --> 00:39:46,200
Guoming,

789
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,600
what I owe you

790
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,280
and mom and dad,

791
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:52,610
