800
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:24,240
About mom and dad,

801
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:25,600
and Erpang too.

802
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:28,360
Every single day.

803
00:40:28,760 --> 00:40:30,000
