808
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:48,000
He hasn't.

809
00:40:50,040 --> 00:40:51,320
We're here for him.

810
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:59,040
Before you leave tomorrow,

811
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,760
could you visit dad?

812
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:03,240
He

813
00:41:04,600 --> 00:41:06,280
really misses you a lot.

814
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:13,120
Guoming,

815
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:16,400
please take care of Erpang for me.

816
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,340
What are you doing?

817
00:42:06,760 --> 00:42:08,160
Why aren't you sleeping?

818
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:09,840
Do you think

819
00:42:11,640 --> 00:42:13,120
my mom loves me?

820
00:42:15,160 --> 00:42:15,760
Of course.

821
00:42:17,200 --> 00:42:18,720
What mother in this world

822
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:20,120
doesn't love her own son?

823
00:42:23,080 --> 00:42:23,880
Erpang.

824
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:26,560
Adults have

825
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:29,000
their own difficulties.

826
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:30,800
When you grow up,

827
00:42:31,640 --> 00:42:33,440
you'll understand everything.

828
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:35,640
I miss my dad.

829
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:40,000
Your dad will be out soon.

830
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:45,460
Really?

831
00:42:45,760 --> 00:42:46,240
Yes.

832
00:42:46,520 --> 00:42:47,580
In a couple of days.

833
00:42:47,880 --> 00:42:49,040
